'''哈罗德·罗登·布里格斯'''（{{lang-en|'''Harold Rawdon Briggs'''}}，{{bd|1894年|7月24日|1952年|10月27日|catIdx=H}}），[[英属印度陆军|英属印度陆军]]中将，马来亚英军军事指挥官。1950年退役后被召回，担任马来西亚紧急事件马来西亚行动主任，由他制定了“{{Link-en|布里格斯计划|Briggs' Plan}}”，旨在打败[[马来西亚共产党|马来西亚共产党]]开展的农村游击战。<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.npg.org.uk/collections/search/person/mp76787/sir-harold-rawdon-briggs |title=Sir Harold Rawdon Briggs - Person - National Portrait Gallery |accessdate=2020-10-24 |archive-date=2020-10-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201027041630/https://www.npg.org.uk/collections/search/person/mp76787/sir-harold-rawdon-briggs |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://pwencycl.kgbudge.com/B/r/Briggs_Rawdon.htm |title=The Pacific War Online Encyclopedia: Briggs, H. Rawdon |accessdate=2020-10-24 |archive-date=2020-10-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201026194928/http://pwencycl.kgbudge.com/B/r/Briggs_Rawdon.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=https://enacademic.com/dic.nsf/enwiki/6680620 |title=Harold Rawdon Briggs |accessdate=2020-10-24 |archive-date=2020-10-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201026061801/https://enacademic.com/dic.nsf/enwiki/6680620 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.oxforddnb.com/view/10.1093/ref:odnb/9780198614128.001.0001/odnb-9780198614128-e-95631 |title=Briggs, Sir Harold Rawdon (1894–1952), army officer |accessdate=2020-10-24 |archive-date=2020-10-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201027105459/https://www.oxforddnb.com/view/10.1093/ref:odnb/9780198614128.001.0001/odnb-9780198614128-e-95631 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

